<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="updated">Last updated: June 30, 2026</p>

<p>Buzz ("we", "our", or "us") operates buzzfinder.app and the Buzz mobile application. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our service.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<p><strong>Account Information:</strong> When you create an account, we collect your email address and a password (stored securely via Supabase authentication).</p>
<p><strong>Location Information:</strong> With your permission, we use your device's GPS location to show events near you. We do not store your location on our servers.</p>
<p><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We collect anonymous analytics data including pages visited and general usage patterns via Vercel Analytics. This data contains no personally identifiable information.</p>
<p><strong>User Content:</strong> Event reviews, star ratings, attendance confirmations, and events you submit are stored in our database and may be visible to other users.</p>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<ul>
  <li>To provide and improve the Buzz service</li>
  <li>To show you local events near your location</li>
  <li>To maintain your account and preferences</li>
  <li>To display your reviews and attendance to other users</li>
</ul>

<h2>Third Party Services</h2>
<p>Buzz uses the following third party services to provide event data:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Ticketmaster</strong> — event data (developer.ticketmaster.com)</li>
  <li><strong>SerpAPI</strong> — Google Events data (serpapi.com)</li>
  <li><strong>PredictHQ</strong> — event intelligence (predicthq.com)</li>
  <li><strong>RapidAPI</strong> — additional event sources (rapidapi.com)</li>
  <li><strong>OpenStreetMap</strong> — mapping and geocoding (openstreetmap.org)</li>
</ul>
<p>Each of these services has their own privacy policy governing the data they collect.</p>

<h2>Data Storage</h2>
<p>Your account data is stored securely using Supabase, a PostgreSQL database provider. We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

<h2>Data Deletion</h2>
<p>You may request deletion of your account and associated data at any time by contacting us at privacy@buzzfinder.app.</p>

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>Buzz is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at: <a href="mailto:privacy@buzzfinder.app">privacy@buzzfinder.app</a></p>
